{"tid":1612971,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"核彈 印尼籍女記者證實右眼將永久失明","createTime":"2019-10-02T11:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T12:28:39.000Z","uid":312362,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"eb4600f5a50c9bfa35cecf1504e3456733c78a28","tid":1612971,"uid":312362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:53:07.000Z","msg":"9.29當日在灣仔採訪期間被警員射中右眼的印尼籍女記者Veby Mega Indah證實右眼將永久失明。其代表律師Michael Vidler表示，醫生證實Veby的右眼球爆裂，造成永久失明，損傷的比例須待手術後方能評估。Vidler指，他已從第三方獲得證據，射擊至Veby右眼的是橡膠子彈，而非早前相信的布袋彈。Veby的家人現時已在香港及陪伴她身旁。<br />\n<br />\nVeby上周日在灣仔採訪時，被警方發射的子彈射中右眼，當時她穿著印有「PRESS（傳媒」）的背心及頭盔，以及戴上記者證，能夠明顯辨識為記者。Veby送院後，Vidler發聲明指將提出刑事及民意訴訟，以追究警務處處長及涉事警員的責任。"},{"pid":"9270c425634d3e253d95434e87d5a05db785be83","tid":1612971,"uid":236368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:53:54.000Z","msg":"支持印尼排華"},{"pid":"57ac1818fe07d27134877a5291333ac9f04ee0be","tid":1612971,"uid":312362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:54:14.000Z","msg":"On9黑警 煲大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c3d78863fb61bc222ac1719aaaebe23a08ad46","tid":1612971,"uid":204864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:54:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be0fdef4bf347add9672469f9d3bdcd195599cb6","tid":1612971,"uid":7358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:54:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6fd5da9505c7f0e436cc87a9e7ce3a6dde97828","tid":1612971,"uid":134913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:54:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae83252